title: Kylie and Garibay
text:
Kylie and Garibay (stylized as Kylie + Garibay) are a musical duo composed of Australian singer-songwriter Kylie Minogue and American record producer Fernando Garibay. The duo are based in Los Angeles, California, U.S., where Garibay's home studio is located. Their debut extended play (EP), Sleepwalker (2014), was accompanied by a short film directed by English fashion designer William Baker, and was presented at Minogue's fourteenth concert tour, the Kiss Me Once Tour. Sleepwalker was followed by the duo's self-titled EP (2015), which contained guest appearances from Jamaican musician Shaggy, Australian singer Sam Sparro, and Italian record producer Giorgio Moroder.
